title: Simple Assessment Techniques for Soil and Water
description:
This 37 pages booklet was prepared for a workshop on environmental factors in small-scale development projects in 1980 by Dr. Timothy S. Wood then director of environmental studies, Wright State University.


This file was found on the cd3wd liberary http://www.cd3wd.com/
